\"Dead or Anything\"<br />{{small|(as part of Dando Lee Petersson Schwartzman)}}\n| 2002\n| ''Dando Lee Petersson Schwartzman''\n|-\n! scope=\"row\"| \"[[In My Life]]\"\n| 2005\n| ''[[This Bird Has Flown \u2013 A 40th Anniversary Tribute to the Beatles' Rubber Soul]]''\n|-\n! scope=\"row\"| \"American Television\"\n| 2008\n| ''[[Ripe (Ben Lee album)|Ripe]]''\n|-\n! scope=\"row\"| \"What's So Bad (About Feeling Good)?\"\n| 2009\n| ''[[The Rebirth of Venus]]''\n|-\n! scope=\"row\"| \"Forgiveness\"\n| rowspan=\"3\"| 2015\n| rowspan=\"3\"| ''[[Love Is the Great Rebellion]]''\n|-\n! scope=\"row\"| \"The Body of Love\"\n|-\n! scope=\"row\"| \"Goodbye to Yesterday\"\n|-\n|}\n\n===Other appearances===\n* \"Make Your Move\" (featuring [[Ione Skye]]) from ''[[Spider (2007 film)|Spider]]'' (2007)\n* \"Beautiful Flirt\" (with Ione Skye and Jack Graddis) from ''[[Bear (2011 film)|Bear]]'' (2011)\n\n==Awards and nominations==\n\n===Awards===\n*[[ARIA Music Awards of 2005|2005 ARIA Music Awards]], Single of the Year \u2013 \"[[Catch My Disease]]\"\n*2005 ARIA Music Awards, Best Male Artist for ''[[Awake Is the New Sleep]]''\n*2005 ARIA Music Awards, Best Independent Release for ''[[Awake Is the New Sleep]]''\n*2005 ARIA Music Awards, Best Cover Art for ''[[Awake Is the New Sleep]]''\n*[[APRA Awards of 2006|2006 APRA Music Awards]], Song of the Year \u2013 \"[[Catch My Disease]]\"<ref name=\"SongWin\">{{cite web | url = http://www.apra-amcos.com.au/APRAAwards/APRASongoftheYear/PreviousWinners.aspx | title = Previous Winners Song of the Year | publisher = [[Australasian Performing Right Association]] (APRA) | accessdate = 5 May 2010 }}</ref>\n*2006 APRA Music Awards, Most Performed Australian Work \u2013 \"[[Catch My Disease]]\"<ref name=\"APRAWin2006\">{{cite web | url = http://www.apra-amcos.com.au/APRAAwards/MusicAwards/History/2006Winners.aspx | title = 2006 Winners \u2013 APRA Music Awards | publisher = Australasian Performing Right Association (APRA) | accessdate = 5 May 2010 